application.controller

Class RingUpCustomerController

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.controller.RingUpCustomerController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, javafx.event.EventHandler

    public class RingUpCustomerController
extends Object
implements javafx.event.EventHandler
    The controller for ringing customers up. This screen is called to track how much money the customer is paying, checking to see if the customer paid enough, then printing a receipt.
    Author:
    Darean Wilde grl167 63678621, Jacob Shawver fww704 36242636, Majerus Sims hug180 79595196, Alexander Delgado tvh991 79595706

                 throws IOException
